cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with head pose estimation from a single 2D face image using geometry-based algorithms. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a likely category as the paper involves 3D facial models and morphing of feature points in 3D space. 
3. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as head pose estimation is an important aspect of human-computer interaction. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and analysis. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as head pose estimation is important in robotics for tasks such as object recognition and tracking.
